{"decision": "RejectOffer"} 

**Reasoning:**

Alice is clearly trying to create a sense of urgency and hype the value, even though she knows her product is worth less to her ($1,200,000) than your absolute maximum ($1,500,000).  By rejecting her offer, you put yourself in a stronger negotiating position. You have a backup option (John) and Alice would lose the sale if you go with him.
